beer.beer_description:
NOTE: This is branded "Stout" in bottle and draft and "The Fuggle is Real" in cans. 

At 5.8% ABV and 58 IBUs, “The Fuggle is Real” is a stout you can approach without too much trepidation.  We’ve used some US Loral hops in combination with Fuggle hops and a rich, chocolatey malt bill to get that noble, earthy, dark fruit quality that provides the signature Creatures stoutyness.  Stoutyness is goodliness indeed.
